item.title: Melbourne's Graffiti Laneways
item.description:
Melbourne's Graffiti Laneways

Melbourne's Graffiti Laneways Episode: Vlog_06 Melbourne city is known for its rich art culture, tag along and join Dave as he explores the city while filming with YHA for a film project. Exploring some of Melbourne's best graffiti laneways such as Hozier Lane.

item.title: Return To Rio Festival
item.description:
Return To Rio Festival

Return To Rio Festival Episode: Vlog_07 Return to Rio Festival was absouletly amazing, what a crazy festival to go to just outside of Sydney in Wisemans Ferry area. The costumes and outfits where amazing, everyone put in such great effort. The Djs and event setup was spectaular as well.

item.title: Cinematic Sessions // A Journey Through Japan
item.description:
Cinematic Sessions // A Journey Through Japan

The country that has stolen my heart. This is the first CINEMATIC SESSIONS series of DAVODAYS. Cinematic sessions will be highlighted travel, documentary and profile videos of the the highest quality. This episode is dedicated to an amazing experience travelling through Japan over two weeks. Japan is such an incredible place to travel.

item.title: Sculptures by the Sea
item.description:
Sculptures by the Sea

Sculptures by the Sea Episode: Vlog_03 Hey Guys, Check out a fun day exploring Sydney's Eastern Beaches and the famous Sculptures by the Sea exhibition, including world famous sculptors from all over the world. The vlog eventually ends up in a classic house halloween party.

item.title: Sydney Australia's Best Hidden Secret
item.description:
Sydney Australia's Best Hidden Secret

Sydney Australia's Best Hidden Secret Episode: Vlog_03 Hey Guys, Sydney is famous for its harbour, so why not explore it all. Tag along as i explore some of Sydney's Best Hidden Secrets in Sydney Harbour. These are the top places in Sydney to see and discover.
